e7525c87960eefe77ee4cc.avif?t=1774024650\" width=616 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/4dfff31a3ea86be08e1b055e2d6a0151.poster.avif?t=1774024650\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/4dfff31a3ea86be08e1b055e2d6a0151.webm?t=1774024650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/4dfff31a3ea86be08e1b055e2d6a0151.mp4?t=1774024650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Experience multiple twists on classic platforming. Master creative arcade elements, such as rhythm-driven musical slides and magnetic gameplay, as you explore and conquer challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/7059b00b76498668fb93e28371829f57.avif?t=1774024650\" width=616 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/65c60e0b749d9457bb40dc7d6f1dba5f.poster.avif?t=1774024650\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/65c60e0b749d9457bb40dc7d6f1dba5f.webm?t=1774024650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/65c60e0b749d9457bb40dc7d6f1dba5f.mp4?t=1774024650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Joining Boti are his charming nanobot companions, aptly named Zero and One. Zero is the calm, cool, and collected robo helper while One basically has no off switch. Each main character is fully voiced and oozing with charm and personality.</p>",
